_ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _

ATTENTION: I'm really sorry to anounce that there's a little bug in a couple of CT's spawn points...i will fix this problem this weekend and re-release the map as 1.2 version.


_ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _

1.1 - here is a list of fixes i've made:

-cubemaps
-texture misalignments
-props in the bombsite B
-fps optimization (could be optimized better...anyone can help me with fps optimization?)
-light optimization
-custom decals
-a bit of detail here and there
_ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _



Interesting lights and town architecture.

Unfortunately screenshots are not sufficient to have a good idea of this map, due to it's particular layout...download it and take a look to see with your eyes!

Have Fun!
